          "content": "**Undirected Graph:**\n\n```\n    [1]---[2]\n     |    /|\n     |   / |\n     |  /  |\n    [5]---[4]---[3]\n         /\n        /\n```\n\n**Adjacency List (Undirected):**\n\n| Vertex | Neighbors |\n|--------|-----------|\n| 1 | 2 → 5 |\n| 2 | 1 → 5 → 3 → 4 |\n| 3 | 2 → 4 |\n| 4 | 2 → 5 → 3 |\n| 5 | 4 → 1 → 2 |\n\n**Adjacency Matrix (Undirected):**\n\n|   | 1 | 2 | 3 | 4 | 5 |\n|---|---|---|---|---|---|\n| 1 | 0 | 1 | 0 | 0 | 1 |\n| 2 | 1 | 0 | 1 | 1 | 1 |\n| 3 | 0 | 1 | 0 | 1 | 0 |\n| 4 | 0 | 1 | 1 | 0 | 1 |\n| 5 | 1 | 1 | 0 | 1 | 0 |\n\n**Directed Graph:**\n\n```\n    [1]--->[2]<---[3]\n     |      |      |\n     v      v      v\n    [4]<---[5]    [6]-->(self-loop)\n           ^\n           |\n          (from 3)\n```\n\n**Adjacency List (Directed):**\n\n| Vertex | Out-neighbors |\n|--------|---------------|\n| 1 | 2 → 4 |\n| 2 | 5 |\n| 3 | 6 → 5 |\n| 4 | 2 |\n| 5 | 4 |\n| 6 | 6 |\n\n**Adjacency Matrix (Directed):**\n\n|   | 1 | 2 | 3 | 4 | 5 | 6 |\n|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|\n| 1 | 0 | 1 | 0 | 1 | 0 | 0 |\n| 2 | 0 | 0 | 0 | 0 | 1 | 0 |\n| 3 | 0 | 0 | 0 | 0 | 1 | 1 |\n| 4 | 0 | 1 | 0 | 0 | 0 | 0 |\n| 5 | 0 | 0 | 0 | 1 | 0 | 0 |\n| 6 | 0 | 0 | 0 | 0 | 0 | 1 |"
